v \in H_0^1(\Omega)
\{u_n\}_{n \in \mathbb{N}}'
L^2(0,T; H_0^1)
0 \leq t \leq t+a \leq T
(u_n(t+a)-u_n(t),v)_{L^2(\Omega)}=\int_{\Omega} (u_n(t+a)-u_n(t))vdx= \int_{\Omega} \left(\int_t^{t+a}u_n'(s)ds \right)vdx= \int_t^{t+a} \int_{\Omega}u_n'(s)vdx ds= \int_t^{t+a} \langle u_n'(s),v \rangle_{(H_0^1)' H_0^1} ds,
